title: Notable Week 2 Matchups
description:
Wendi Nix, Eddie Royal, and Stanford Steve Coughlin preview some notable week 2 matchups including No. 1 Alabama vs Texas, No. 24 Tennessee vs No. 17 Pitt, and No. 20 Kentucky vs No. 12 Florida. Plus, Tiffany Greene and Jay Walker are joined by Tennessee State head coach Eddie George for a weekly update of HBCU football.
